# Adaptive sampling



Plot function

::: {#6c4c3c90 .cell execution_count=2}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
function doplot(xy)
    f = cm.lines(xy)
    cm.scatter!(xy, color=:darkred, markersize=5)
    return f
end;
```
:::


Linear function

::: {#8f886799 .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
sampleadaptive(x -> x, -1, 1) |> doplot
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=4}
